                     352 (SAe 68, 69)], no. III)&#xD; III) Homily by Cyriacus of Behnesa on the
                     Assumption of Mary (fols. 156ra-188vb) (cp. V. ARRAS, De Transitu Mariae
                     apocrypha aethiopice II, Louvain 1974 [CSCO 351, 352 (SAe 68, 69)], no.
                     IV)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
